title: United States 30 Year TIPS Yield
description: 30 Year TIPS Yield was 1.66 percent on Thursday November 10, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the United States 30 Year TIPS Yield reached an all time high of 4.40 in January of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United States 30 Year TIPS Yield.
author: Federal Reserve
